snippet: The two rival parties claiming victory in Cambodia’s general election reached an agreement for a joint investigation of polling irregularities, but one side’s commitment soon appeared to waver.
lead_paragraph: The two rival parties claiming victory in Cambodia’s general election reached an agreement for a joint investigation of polling irregularities, but one side’s commitment soon appeared to waver.

headline.main: Rival Parties in Cambodia Agree to Investigate Election Results
headline.print_headline: Rival Parties in Cambodia Agree To Investigate Election Results
